  "texts": [
    "Here we show how to extend BP-OSD to the circuit-based noise model, see the Supplementary Information for details.",
    "Our approach closely follows refs. 45-48.",
    "A noisy version of the syndrome measurement circuit may include several types of faulty operations such as memory errors on idle data or check qubits, faulty CNOT gates, qubit initializations and measurements.",
    "We consider the circuit-based noise model 10 in which each operation fails independently with probability p. The probability of a logical error p L depends on the error rate p, details of the syndrome measurement circuits, and the decoding algorithm.",
    "Let P L (N c) be the logical error probability after performing N c syndrome cycles."
